Full stack Software Engineer

$47.00/hr

Copy link to clipboard
I'm a passionate software developer who started this journey because of my love for video games and the desire to create them. While game development captured my heart in 2018-2019, I discovered a deeper passion for software development as a profession, and I've been building solutions ever since. My expertise lies in web development, where I thrive on challenging and unconventional projects. I'm not interested in typical store appsI seek complex problems that push my skills forward. I also excel at creating beautiful, functional Windows Forms applications for streamlined, elegant solutions. Beyond web development, I enjoy mobile development with a focus on creating visually appealing, responsive web-based experiences. As an AI enthusiast, I love leveraging Claude's capabilities to write smarter, more efficient code. Technology fascinates meespecially emerging and futuristic innovations. I'm driven by curiosity and a desire to stay at the forefront of development trends. On a personal note, I'm a devoted Christian and happily married to my wonderful wife for nearly 5 years. We have a beautiful daughter who's almost 10 months old, and life couldn't be better. I'm 30 years old, living in the stunning mountain town of Jarabacoa, Dominican Republic. The natural beauty, freedom to explore, pristine rivers, amazing weather, wonderful views, and warm community here inspire my creativity daily.

January 2024 - Present
Developed and deployed a fully automated trading bot with proprietary trading strategy on Binance.com. The bot operates 24/7 autonomously while being completely monitored and managed through Telegram integration. Features include real-time strategy monitoring, automated position management, risk controls, and performance tracking via Telegram notifications and commands. The bot executes trades based on the custom strategy with minimal manual intervention.

Full Stack Developer - JCM (Report Card Management System) | Self-Employed (JCM Project)

January 2023 - Present
Developed and architected a comprehensive school report card management system (JCM) since 2023 with two partners. This full-featured platform enables schools, students, parents, and tutors to manage and access student report cards, grades, test scores, and feedback from teachers in real-time. Built with modern web technologies to provide secure and intuitive user experiences for all stakeholders in the educational ecosystem. Features include role-based access control, analytics dashboards, notification systems, and integration capabilities with educational institutions.
